annotations.label: Page-header
annotations.text: Official Journal of the European Union

annotations.label: Text
annotations.text: Pursuant to article 26(2) of the Financial Regulation of the European Training Foundation (ETF) adopted by the Management Board on 17 June 2003, the budget and amending budgets, as finally adopted, shall be published in the Official Journal of the European Union within two months of their adoption.
annotations.translation: 根据管理委员会于 2003 年 6 月 17 日通过的《欧洲培训基金会 (ETF) 财务条例》第 26(2) 条，最终通过的预算和修正预算应在通过后的两个月内在《欧盟官方公报》上公布。

annotations.label: Text
annotations.text: The first amending budget of the ETF for 2005 was adopted by the Management Board following a written procedure that took place between 18 October 2005 and 2 November 2005 (ETF-GB-029-01).
annotations.translation: 在 2005 年 10 月 18 日至 2005 年 11 月 2 日期间，管理委员会经由书面程序通过了 2005 年的第一个修正预算 (ETF-GB-029-01)。

annotations.label: Caption
annotations.text: For complete details about 2005 budget and establishment plan please visit ETF website at the following address: www.etf.eu.int (Documentation Centre - Institutional reports)
annotations.translation: 有关 2005 年预算和建立计划的完整详细信息，请访问 ETF 网站：www.etf.eu.int （文献中心 - 机构报告）
